headline: Royal Caribbean Group Raises Dividend Thirty Three Percent
summary: The Board of Directors of Royal Caribbean Cruises Ltd. (NYSE: RCL) today declared a quarterly dividend of $1.00 per common share payable on October 13, 2025 to shareholders of record at the close of business on September 25, 2025.
